          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 82602,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Manchmal müssen wir Daten innerhalb eines Strings aktualisieren, ohne einen komplett neuen String zu erstellen. Zum Beispiel, um ein tägliches Mittagsspecial zu aktualisieren.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"special = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Today's special is pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Replace",
            "id": 82603,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Wir können einen Teil eines Strings, der in einer Variable gespeichert ist, ersetzen, indem wir zuerst den Namen der Variable und die Anweisung <code>replace()</code> codieren.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"special = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Today's special is pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"new_special = special.replace()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"67\" /><option startIndex=\"67\" endIndex=\"68\" /><option startIndex=\"68\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>replace</code>, gefolgt von <code>(</code> und schließlich <code>)</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Values",
            "id": 82604,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Innerhalb der Klammern fügen wir den Teil hinzu, den wir ersetzen möchten, wie <code>\"pasta\"</code>, ein Komma und dann den neuen Wert, <code>\"pizza\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"special = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Today's special is pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"new_special = special.replace(\" /><text value=\"&quot;pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\",\" /><text value=\"&quot;pizza&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"68\" endIndex=\"75\" /><option startIndex=\"75\" endIndex=\"76\" /><option startIndex=\"76\" endIndex=\"83\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>\"pasta\"</code>, gefolgt von <code>,</code> und schließlich <code>\"pizza\"</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Displaying",
            "id": 82628,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Durch das Codieren von <code>print(new_special)</code> können wir sehen, dass die Variable <code>new_special</code> den aktualisierten String enthält.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"special = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Today's special is pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"new_special = special.replace(\" /><text value=\"&quot;pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\",\" /><text value=\"&quot;pizza&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(new_special)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"86\" endIndex=\"91\" /><option startIndex=\"91\" endIndex=\"92\" /><option startIndex=\"92\" endIndex=\"103\" /><option startIndex=\"103\" endIndex=\"104\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Today's special is pizza\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>print</code>, gefolgt von <code>(</code> und schließlich <code>new_special</code>, <code>)</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "No change",
            "id": 82630,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Durch das Codieren von <code>print(special)</code> können wir sehen, dass sich der Wert der ursprünglichen Variable nicht ändert.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"special = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Today's special is pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"new_special = special.replace(\" /><text value=\"&quot;pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\",\" /><text value=\"&quot;pizza&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(new_special)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(special)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"106\" endIndex=\"120\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Today's special is pizza\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Today's special is pasta\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Gib <code>print(special)</code> ein.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Update",
            "id": 82629,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Statt eine neue Variable zu erstellen, können wir die ursprüngliche Variable der aktualisierten Zeichenkette zuweisen, indem wir <code>special</code> codieren. </p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"special = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Today's special is pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"special = special.replace(\" /><text value=\"&quot;pasta&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\",\" /><text value=\"&quot;pizza&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(special)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"38\" endIndex=\"45\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Today's special is pizza\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Gib <code>special</code> ein.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Occurrences ",
            "id": 82612,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Wenn wir <code>replace()</code> so verwenden, werden alle Vorkommen des Wertes innerhalb des Strings ersetzt. Das können wir hier sehen, indem wir <code>print(july)</code> codieren.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"june = \" /><text value=\"&quot;June sales target updated. Let's rock June!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"july = june.replace(\" /><text value=\"&quot;June&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;July&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(july)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"91\" endIndex=\"96\" /><option startIndex=\"96\" endIndex=\"97\" /><option startIndex=\"97\" endIndex=\"101\" /><option startIndex=\"101\" endIndex=\"102\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"July sales target updated. Let's rock July!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>print</code>, gefolgt von <code>(</code> und schließlich <code>july</code>, <code>)</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
