            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Aktualisiere den String, indem du <code>replace()</code> aufrufst, um den Fehler bei der Großschreibung zu beheben</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"answer = \" /><text value=\"&quot;The answer is INcorrect&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"updated = answer.replace(\" /><text value=\"&quot;INcorrect&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\",\" /><text value=\"&quot;incorrect&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(updated)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"73\" endIndex=\"84\" /><option startIndex=\"46\" endIndex=\"52\" /><option startIndex=\"52\" endIndex=\"53\" /><option startIndex=\"53\" endIndex=\"60\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"The answer is incorrect\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>answer</code>, gefolgt von <code>.</code> und schließlich <code>replace</code>, <code>\"incorrect\"</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
